Ranger Help for: rebuild
========================

SYNTAX:      rebuild quiver
USAGE:       Anywhere.

SUMMARY:
Creates a brand new quiver if you have lost yours. Your quiver is
the physical manifestation of your bond with the Rangers guild and
is required for most guild commands to work.

If your quiver exists but is malfunctioning, use 'repair quiver'
instead.

